== About
I am pursuing a B.Sc. in Statistics at CUHK-Shenzhen. I am currently a research
assistant working with a PhD student in the research group of Prof. Dr. Ruoyu
Sun. My work mainly focuses on optimization for deep learning.

I use this website to keep a concise academic profile, collect research notes,
and organize reading related to optimization, statistics, and machine learning.

== Research Interests
- Optimization theory.
- Optimization for machine learning.
- Machine learning theory.
- Deep learning optimization.

== Education
- *B.Sc. in Statistics*, School of Data Science, The Chinese University of Hong
  Kong, Shenzhen, Sept. 2025 -- May 2029 (expected).

== Experience
- *Research Assistant*, CUHK-Shenzhen, May 2026 -- present. Working with a PhD
  student in the research group of Prof. Dr. Ruoyu Sun, mainly focusing on
  optimization for deep learning.

