== MathJax
This site is built with jemdoc+MathJax. For example, gradient descent studies
updates of the form

\(
\theta_{t+1} = \theta_t - \eta \nabla f(\theta_t),
\)

and asks how assumptions on $f$ determine convergence behavior.
